d 2002, episodes \"Goofy's Menu Magic\" and \"House of Turkey\")\n*''Mickeypalooza'' (2003, television special) as Piglet (voice)\n*''Winnie the Pooh: ABC's'' (2004) as Piglet (voice)<ref name=\"Voice\">{{cite web| url=http://www.behindthevoiceactors.com/John-Fiedler/| title=John Fiedler| website=Behind the Voice Actors| accessdate=18 April 2019}}</ref>\n*''Winnie the Pooh: 123s'' (2004) as Piglet (voice)<ref name=\"Voice\"/>\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Video games===\n*''The Book of Pooh: A Story Without A Tail'' (2002) as Piglet (voice)\n*''[[Kingdom Hearts (video game)|Kingdom Hearts]]'' (2002) as Piglet (voice)\n*''[[Piglet's Big Game]]'' (2003) as Piglet (voice)\n*''[[Winnie the Pooh's Rumbly Tumbly Adventure]]'' (2005) as Piglet (voice)\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{IMDb name|275835}}\n*{{IBDB name|71786}}\n*{{iobdb name|13662}}\n{{Memoryalpha}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Fiedler, John}}\n[[Category:1925 births]]\n[[Category:2005 deaths]]\n[[Category:Male actors from Wisconsin]]\n[[Category:American male film actors]]\n[[Category:American male radio actors]]\n[[Category:American male stage actors]]\n[[Category:American male television actors]]\n[[Category:American male voice actors]]\n[[Category:Deaths from cancer in New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Deaths from cancer of unknown primary origin]]\n[[Category:Marshall University alumni]]\n[[Category:American people of German descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Irish descent]]\n[[Category:People from Englewood, New Jersey]]\n[[Category:People from Platteville, Wisconsin]]\n[[Category:20th-century American male actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century American male actors]]\n[[Category:People from Shorewood, Wisconsin]]\n[[Category:Military personnel from Wisconsin]]\n[[Category:American naval personnel of World War II]]\n[[Category:Male actors of German descent]]\n", "name_user": "Koconnorc", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eDeath", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Fi