ois]]: [[Good News Publishers|Crossway Books]], 1997.\n*''Cosmic Christmas: An Angel's Story'', [[Dallas, Texas]]: Word Publishing, 1997.\n*''The Greatest Moments'', [[Dallas, Texas]]: Word Publishing, 1997.\n*''The Cross'', [[Portland, Oregon]]: [[Random House|Multnomah Press]], 1998.\n*''The Heart of Christmas'', 1998.\n*''Just Like Jesus'', [[Dallas, Texas]]: Word Publishing, 1998.\n*''The Christmas Cross'', [[Dallas, Texas]]: Word Publishing, 1998. (the 2003 American Christian film, ''[[Christmas Child]]'', was based on this short story)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/christmas-child-max-lucado/1100330991|website=B&N.com Review |title=Christmas Child: A Story of Coming Home}}</ref>\n*''Let the Journey Begin'', [[Dallas, Texas]]: Word Publishing, 1998.\n*''When Christ Comes'', [[Dallas, Texas]]: Word Publishing, 1999.\n*''Just the Way Your Are'', [[Wheaton, Illinois]]: [[Good News Publishers|Crossway Books]], 1999. \n*''The Gift for All People'', [[Portland, Oregon]]: [[Random House|Multnomah Press]], 1999.\n*''Opening Windows'', 1999.\n*''Because I Love You'', [[Wheaton, Illinois]]: [[Good News Publishers|Crossway Books]], 1999.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ecpa.org/christianbookawards/gm2000.php|title=Christian Book Award\u00ae - ECPA|website=www.ecpa.org|accessdate=April 2, 2018}}</ref>\n*''Topical Bible Study Series'', 1999-2000.\n*''He Chose the Nails'', [[Dallas, Texas]]: Word Publishing, 2000.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ecpa.org/christianbookawards/gm2001.php|title=Christian Book Award\u00ae - ECPA|website=www.ecpa.org|accessdate=April 2, 2018}}</ref>\n*''[[Grace for the Moment]]'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|J. Countryman]], 2000.\n*''In the Footsteps of Jesus'', [[Carol Stream, Illinois]]: [[Tyndale House]], 2000.\n*''He Did This Just For You'', 2000.\n*''Small Gifts in God's Hands'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|Thomas Nelson]], 2000.\n*''Traveling Light'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|W Publishing Group]], 2001.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ecpa.org/christianbookawards/gm2002.php|title=Christian Book Award\u00ae - ECPA|website=www.ecpa.org|accessdate=April 2, 2018}}</ref>\n*''Traveling Light Journal'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|W Publishing Group]], 2001.\n*''America Looks Up'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|W Publishing Group]], 2001.\n*''One Incredible Moment'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|J. Countryman]], 2001.\n*''Safe in the Shepherd's Arms'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|J. Countryman]], 2001.\n*''Just For You'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|W Publishing Group]], 2002.\n*''A Love Worth Giving'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|W Publishing Group]], 2002.\n*''Traveling Light for Mothers'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|W Publishing Group]], 2002.\n*''He Chose You'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|Thomas Nelson]], 2002.\n*''Just Like Jesus (Devotional)'', 2002.\n*''A Heart Like Jesus'', 2002.\n*''What the Cross Means to Me'', 2002.\n*''Next Door Savior'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|W Publishing Group]], 2003.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ecpa.org/christianbookawards/gm2004.php|title=Christian Book Award\u00ae - ECPA|website=www.ecpa.org|accessdate=April 2, 2018}}</ref>\n*''Experiencing the Heart of Jesus'',<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ecpa.org/christianbookawards/gm2004.php|title=Christian Book Award\u00ae - ECPA|website=www.ecpa.org|accessdate=April 2, 2018}}</ref>\n*''God Thinks You're Wonderful'', 2003. [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|J. Countryman]], 2003.\n*''[[Hermie and Friends|Hermie, A Common Caterpillar]]'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|Thomas Nelson]], 2003. {{ISBN|1-4003-0126-2}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.christianbook.com/hermie-friends-board-books-common-caterpillar/max-lucado/9781400301263/pd/301262|title=Hermie and Friends Board Books, Hermie: A Common Caterpillar|publisher=|accessdate=April 2, 2018|via=www.christianbook.com}}</ref>\n*''It's Not About Me'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|Integrity Publishers]], 2004.<ref>[http://www.ecpa.org/goldmedallion/gm2005.php 2005 Gold Medallion Book Awards Winners - Inspirational] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20071013142243/http://www.ecpa.org/goldmedallion/gm2005.php |date=October 13, 2007 }}</ref>\n*''Come Thirsty'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|W Publishing Group]], 2004.\n*''Everyday Blessings'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|J. Countryman]], 2004.\n*''The Story: The Bible as One Continuing Story of God and His People\" [[Zondervan (publisher)|Zondervan]], 2005, 2008, 2011. Various editions, including Teen Edition {{ISBN|978-0-310-72280-9}}.\n*''Cure for the Common Life'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|W Publishing Group]], 2005.\n*''Turn'', [[Portland, Oregon]]: [[Random House|Multnomah Press]], 2005.\n*''God\u2019s Mirror'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|Integrity Publishers]], 2005.\n*''The Way Home: A Princess Story'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|Thomas Nelson]], 2005.\n*''God\u2019s Promises For You'', 2006. (Updated Edition)\n*''Your Special Gift'', [[Wheaton, Illinois]]: [[Good News Publishers|Crossway Books]], 2006.\n*''Grace For The Moment II'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|J. Countryman]], 2006.\n*''Facing Your Giants'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|W Publishing Group]], 2006.\n*''Every Day Deserves a Chance: Wake Up to the Gift of 24 Hours'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|Thomas Nelson]], 2006.\n*''3:16: The Numbers of Hope'', [[Nashville, Tennessee]]: [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|W Publishing Group]],