/https://twitter.com/SPKCentrs |archive-date=3 February 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|SVK}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Slovakia|Slovakia]]\n|534\n|2\n|8\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|AND}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Andorra|Andorra]]\n|526\n|21\n|31\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|CYP}} <!---deleting from Europe will be considered vandalism and will lead to blocking of account and IP---> [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Cyprus|Cyprus]]\n|455\n|14\n|37\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|ALB}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Albania|Albania]]\n|377\n|21\n|131\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|SMR}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in San Marino|San Marino]]\n|277\n|32\n|40\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.iss.sm/on-line/home/articolo49014186.html |title=Gruppo coordinamento emergenze - aggiornamento 27 marzo |date=2020-03-27 |website=Istituto per la Sicurezza Sociale |language=it |access-date=2020-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327134149/http://www.iss.sm/on-line/home/articolo49014186.html |archive-date=27 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|Malta}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Malta|Malta]]\n|241\n|0\n|5\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|MNE}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Montenegro|Montenegro]]\n|233\n|2\n|1\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|KOS}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Kosovo|Kosovo]]\n|170\n|4\n|24\n|<ref>{{Citation |title=2020 coronavirus pandemic in Kosovo |date=2020-03-25 |url=https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=2020_coronavirus_pandemic_in_Kosovo&oldid=947299455 |work=Wikipedia |language=en |access-date=2020-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200406000620/https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=2020_coronavirus_pandemic_in_Kosovo&oldid=947299455 |archive-date=6 April 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|LIE}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Liechtenstein|Liechtenstein]]\n|77\n|1\n|0\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.volksblatt.li/default.aspx |title=Aktuelle Nachrichten aus Liechtenstein - volksblatt.li |website=Liechtensteiner Volksb