ce|113}}\n*[http://memoire-du-cyclisme.eu/annuaires/monde2000.php  Final classification for individuals and teams from memoire-du-cyclisme.eu]\n\n{{UCI Road World Cup}}\n\n[[Category:2000 in road cycling| ]]\n[[Category:UCI Road World Cup (men)]]\n", "text_old": "{{ Infobox cycling season\n<!-- Details -->\n| name          = 2000 UCI Road World Cup\n| edition       = 12\n| competition   = [[UCI Road World Cup]]\n| image         = \n| image_caption = \n| image_alt     = \n| image_size    = \n| dates         = 18 March \u2013 21 October\n| location      = [[Europe]]\n| rounds        = 10\n<!-- Winners -->\n| individual_champion      = {{flagathlete|[[Erik Zabel]]|GER}}\n| individual_champion_team = {{ct|TEL|2000}}\n| teams_champion           = {{ct|MAP|2000}}\n| previous = [[1999 UCI Road World Cup|1999]]\n| next     = [[2001 UCI Road World Cup|2001]]\n}}\nThe '''2000 UCI Road World Cup''' was the twelfth edition of the [[UCI Road World Cup]]. It was won by [[Erik Zabel]].\n\n==Races==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Date\n! Race\n! Country\n! Winner\n! Team\n! Report\n|-\n| 18 March\n| [[Milan\u2013San Remo]]\n| {{ITA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Erik Zabel]]|GER}} \n| {{ct|TEL|2000}}\n| [[2000 Milan\u2013San Remo|Report]]\n|-\n| 2 April\n| [[Tour of Flanders]]\n| {{BEL}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Andrei Tchmil]]|BEL}} \n| {{ct|LOT|2000}}\n| [[2000 Tour of Flanders|Report]]\n|-\n| 9 April\n| [[Paris\u2013Roubaix]]\n| {{FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Johan Museeuw]]|ITA}} \n| {{ct|MAP|2000}}\n| [[2000 Paris\u2013Roubaix|Report]]\n|-\n| 16 April\n| [[Li\u00e8ge\u2013Bastogne\u2013Li\u00e8ge]]\n| {{BEL}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Paolo Bettini]]|ITA}} \n| {{ct|MAP|2000}}\n| [[2000 Li\u00e8ge\u2013Bastogne\u2013Li\u00e8ge|Report]]\n|-\n| 22 April\n| [[Amstel Gold Race]]\n| {{NED}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Erik Zabel]]|GER}} \n| {{ct|TEL|2000}}\n| [[2000 Amstel Gold Race|Report]]\n|-\n| 6 August\n| [[HEW Cyclassics]] \n| {{GER}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Gabriele Missaglia]]|ITA}} \n| {{ct|LAM|2000}}\n| [[2000 HE